title: Week 17 picks & "Go get my lunch"
itunes:title: Week 17 picks & "Go get my lunch"
description:
A room with a couple of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler -- recap the Bengals-Broncos showdown and preview the biggest AFC and NFC matchups in Week 17. Plus, Dan Hanzus and Chris Wesseling join the show to review the 2014 season "Go get my lunch" propositions.
